<dl id="n09129a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n09" href="#n09129a">N09 (VI.B.1)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n09all.htm#n09129a"> 129(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">D</font> city in Heaven / <font face="wake">C</font> &mdash; on E</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">ABEL: <font color="green">[St. Augustine:]</font> &ldquo;<mark>Cain founded a city on earth; but Abel</mark> as a stranger and pilgrim looked forward to the <mark>city</mark> of the saints which is <mark>in heaven</mark>&rdquo; (De Civ. Dei, XV, i). <small> <a name="TCE1" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#TCE1"><cite title="source">Catholic Encyclopaedia</cite></a> (1911) I, 36a</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
